{"tid":807130,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[第五次] 初級日文興趣班","createTime":"2018-09-05T09:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T16:12:31.000Z","uid":175564,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"94e282806d365c067792a01c477ff2f06de3288a","tid":807130,"uid":175564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:37:32.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲好,又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次我地想搞一次正式嘅日文班,係連續4堂。真係會當係語言班咁教。<br />\n我地睇過好多feedback d 巴絲都覺得1堂其實真係學唔到d乜野<br />\n所以今次我地會試下真係正式少少 係日語書抽d 練習出黎比大家做啊,會有功課默書之類。<br />\n另外都會有位係日本留過幾年學嘅導師黎幫手教。<br />\n當然都係會由淺教起,係哩4堂當你唔識日文咁一步一步教上去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一堂 教基本50音。基本 grammar介紹 常見字。<br />\n第二堂 vocab, 名詞, grammar<br />\n第三堂 grammar 形容詞變化<br />\n第四堂 grammar 動詞變化<br />\n因為日文d grammar 都幾複雜所以堂堂都會有grammar講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而今次我地會係出面book房,大約$150/hr<br />\n所以會每位收翻$120 人數我預10個 <br />\n搞手只求打個和,其實只係岩岩好填左條數佢,請見諒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知道邊度有平地方BOOK房都可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外都有個茶果班同攝影班,歡迎大家報名體驗下<br />\n<br />\n報名都係哩到報<br />\n<a href=\"https://finterest.link/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinterest.link%2F&d=UacojdqbEYzd%2Fs7TQUlVLNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7fbd97da\" target=\"_blank\">https://finterest.link/</a><br />\n<br />\n如何申請AC,如何搞活動可以睇翻上兩個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/782923/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/782923/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/790141/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/790141/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2c01ab14fd9961356873b8b3c70612460d3f7820","tid":807130,"uid":184094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3bf